    <string name="review_welcome_screen">Review Welcome Screen</string>
    <string name="app_description">Famiq was born from a simple need — to record family expenses without hassle, without spreadsheets, and without drama.\n\nWe believe that managing family finances should be easy and fun, not a burden. With Famiq, you and your partner can record expenses together, monitor trends, and stay on the same track.\n\nNo excessive features. No annoying notifications. Only what you need — it\'s that simple.</string>
